snippet.title: Amber Heard Reportedly in Talks For an HBO Max Mera Solo Series as Spin-Off From Aquaman
snippet.description:
So apparently Amber Heard is in talks to return as Mera for a solo series on HBO Max. WHY? She’s great as Mera but such a bad person.
